description:
Space Trivia will test your knowledge on our solar system, it's planets and a few other things. Fun (and educational) for all ages!

In Space Trivia you will be asked questions about:
NASA's History
The Solar System
The Planets
The Moon
Astronauts
and more!

More questions being added routinely!
name: Space Trivia
shortDescription: Do you like Outer Space? Space Trivia will test your knowledge with general questions on our solar system and more.
